# Production and PWA (Sahgal Classes)

## Deployment

- **Vercel project:** `sahgal-classes-app-6kq9`
- **Live domain:** `sahgalclasses.com` (custom domain; treat as production)

## PWA — do not break without explicit user request

- **`public/manifest.json`** — keep valid JSON; `start_url`, `display`, `icons` paths matter for installability.
- **`public/sw.js`** — service worker at site root **`/sw.js`** (Vite copies `public/` to build root). Do not rename or move without updating **`index.html`** registration.
- **`index.html`** — preserve:
  - `<link rel="manifest" href="/manifest.json" />`
  - `theme-color` and **`apple-touch-icon`** (`/icon-192.png`)
  - **Favicon:** `/icon-192.png`
  - **Service worker registration** script that calls `navigator.serviceWorker.register('/sw.js')`

## UI / code changes

- Prefer **`/public/...` assets** referenced as root paths (`/icon-192.png`, `/logo.png`, etc.) so production and PWA caching stay consistent.
- Avoid replacing **`index.html`** head blocks for PWA/favicon with framework-only meta unless the user asks to migrate PWA setup.
